<h2 id="live-it-out">Live It Out</h2>
<p class="lead">Start doing. Commit to a step, and live it out this week.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Spend time with God daily in this week’s Bible Plan. <a href="http://go2.lc/enthusiastic">go2.lc/enthusiastic</a></li>
  <li>David trusted, walked with, and worshipped God daily. Share how you’ll take action to grow in one of these areas this week.</li>
</ul>

